1592
01:19:20,870 --> 01:19:21,780
Im lặng!

1593
01:19:24,710 --> 01:19:27,830
♫ So, I make this wish ♫
<font color="#93c9eb">Điều ước nơi lòng này</font>

1594
01:19:27,960 --> 01:19:33,090
♫ So, I make this wish - So, I make this wish ♫
