1630
01:22:20,530 --> 01:22:22,530
Asha.

1631
01:22:22,660 --> 01:22:24,780
Cho anh xin lỗi.

1632
01:22:24,910 --> 01:22:26,740
Thật lòng anh xin lỗi.

1633
01:22:28,700 --> 01:22:31,240
